The user's functional role within the organisation. Manager
permits booking on behalf of the org and issuing student invitations;
Student permits booking for themselves at the org's negotiated rate.

Operational state of the bay. Operational bays are bookable;
Maintenance and Decommissioned bays are blocked from
new bookings and displayed as dark grey on the availability calendar.

Returns the reconfiguration template for the given configuration pair,
or null if no explicit template exists (caller falls back to
